rest_of_day_open: I see it going very relaxed and chill.  My children have a week off from school so we do not have to worry about any tests or projects to complete. critical_positive: I think that we were similar and could relate to each other because of those similarities.  I did not feel like she was judging me at all, she was very engaging and sweet.  I also feel like we are on the same page socially so it was nice to have those things in common.
critical_negative: I dont think that there was anything that didn't work about the conversation that I just had. begin_memory_text: It was her first time doing one of these videos, so we chatted about that for a little while. We talked a bit about COVID and animals. She has a golden retriever and a pug x dachshund mix. She also has a cat!
middle_memory_text: We talked a lot about me having a service dog in training. She asked a lot of questions about how I train him and what he is learning. We also talked about living in Michigan, how I moved to PA, and different areas in Michigan. She lives very close to where I grew up so we had a lot in common in that regard!
end_memory_text: We continued talking a lot about animals, mostly horses. Her daughter rides horses. I told her about Assateague Island being near me, and other different areas close to me. We also talked about how nice of a conversation we had together and how the time flew by!
rest_of_day_open: I am planning to do a lot of house cleaning. We are working on changing up some rooms in our house, so I am motivated to get a big portion of that done so we can finally have things organized. Aside from that, I am hoping to relax and watch a lot of horror movies!
critical_positive: We both grew up in Michigan, so we had a lot in common right away! We also both love animals and have several pets. She was very interested in everything I was talking about and asked a lot of questions which made it very easy to keep the conversation moving.
critical_negative: It's honestly hard to come up with much. Early on she was a little unsure on how to proceed. We also interrupted each other talking a few times (sometimes I couldn't tell she was talking because the video glitched). I don't like interrupting people so I felt bad that I did interrupt her a few times. I also wish I had asked her more questions to give her more time to talk.
